subaward_description: THE CITY OF ORANGE MANAGE FIREWALL SERVICES ENTRY POINT PROTECTION AND BACK-UP DISASTER RECOVERY SERVICES PROJECT WILL PURCHASE A BARRACUDA NETWORKS MANAGED FIREWALL SERVICES AND BACKUP DISASTER INCLUDING ANNUAL CONTRACT.  THIS FUNDING WILL ENABLE ALL THE MUNICIPALITIES TO HAVE THEIR INTERNET ENTRY POINTS MONITORED FOR TERRORISTIC CYBER ATTACKS AND ENHANCE CYBER SECURITY WITH PROVIDED BARRACUDA NETWORKS ENHANCED FIREWALL EQUIPMENT.
